{
  "stem": "422.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only place where people could leave [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after they marched in, in 1939, beginning of '40, 1940, the-- the only place was to go to cross the border to Russia, which was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to swim through a-- swim through a river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father begged me and my sister, we should leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as I was very devoted to my parents, I said, I can't leave and leave you behind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My whole family couldn't live-- leave, because my mother was not strong enough to make that voyage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was sickly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My younger brother began already to suffer from elevated temperature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a case of glands, enlarged glands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A matter of fact, that has brought to his death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We couldn't help him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he got sicker and sicker, and he died in the ghetto, a child of 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was not the one that I could leave them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I won't be able to live over there, not knowing what's going on with you here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's going to happen to you, I'm ready it should happen to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I did wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if I would leave, my sister would leave with me, and I-- maybe she would be alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I remained all by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She was shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The poor girl was shot from an action in the ghetto, when they were catching in 1942-- they were catching people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They blockaded the street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took people to send them to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my sister was already employed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all thought that being employed, we're working for them, they let us live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They won't-- they won't evacuate us to another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
